{"tid":2143672,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"連續兩日有加籍華人判死刑 葉建輝於佛山販毒罪成","createTime":"2020-08-07T08:31:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T12:53:28.000Z","uid":240362,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"058c1607f45b63d8b7bef7c4d571073eb5269573","tid":2143672,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:31:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c/126210\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c%2F126210&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLE2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=4e749e24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rthk_new_c/126210</a><br />\n<br />\n佛山市中級人民法院裁定，加拿大籍華人葉建輝販毒等罪成，判處死刑，沒收全部個人財產，是連續兩日有加籍華人被判死刑。內地傳媒報道，法院裁定葉建輝「運輸、製造毒品罪」，一審罪成，案中另一被告盧漢昌，與葉建輝同樣被判死刑；同案另外4人被判無期徒刑，至有期徒刑7年不等。案情指出，葉建輝等6人，與他人合謀製造、運輸毒品。公安機關在被告房間內，發現含有200公斤搖頭丸成分的白色晶體，將多人拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n2020-08-07 16:25:30"},{"pid":"878f6b678a5bec8c2068132754943aa4b5cdc083","tid":2143672,"uid":20867,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:35:03.000Z","msg":"大把中國官員及其家屬子女有外國藉<br />\n<br />\n日日處決<br />\n<br />\n可以殺足十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1fa96cccee1da1e4da42615b547405d1fdc452","tid":2143672,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"878f6b678a5bec8c2068132754943aa4b5cdc083","tid":2143672,"uid":20867,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:35:03.000Z","msg":"大把中國官員及其家屬子女有外國藉<br />\n<br />\n日日處決<br />\n<br />\n可以殺足十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:38:28.000Z","msg":"要連坐滅族都唔過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgm